SWDIV_SWDIV32 
 * @file    SWDIV/SWDIV32/readme.txt
 * @version V1.00
 * @date    2015-12-01
 * @brief   Description of Division example.
Example Description:

This example shows how to use the Division library.

Directory Contents:
  • SWDIV/SWDIV32/main.c Main program
  • SWDIV/SWDIV32/ht32fxxxx_it.c Interrupt handlers
Hardware and Software Environment:
  • This example can be run on HT32 Series development board.
